{
  "stem": "3331.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he went to the Jews, and he said, well, give me this, give me this, give me this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And before the war, he was living with everybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and, and then he came to my father, and he said, he needs for the commandant bohnen kaffee.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Bohnen-- coffee beans were very important for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't have it in Germany, and they liked coffee bean.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father had coffee beans in his business, so he came-- so my father gave him a kilo.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The next day he said, I want two kilos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then he said, I want four kilos, and so on and on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So once I saw him, and I said, look, even a well, if you take out water, it will run dry.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't do it to my father, because I will take-- I will do-- and I threatened him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right away, he went to the German commandant, and he told them that I am very dangerous for the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That before the war, I was in the Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know about the Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was with peyes And Jews, usually in a small town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have communists.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And especially, my father was a rich man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they said that they're going to arrest me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I found out about it, so I run away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I run away to Russia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went-- it was illegal on the border.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was in Russia three months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where were you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Lemberg, Lwow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Russia.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I started to do a little business-- black market.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in Russia, I-- in, in Lemberg, I saw that I will accomplish my two dreams.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why two dreams?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In this time, I was not religious anymore, so I enlisted in a gymnasium, in Lemberg.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
